== 技術風格 ==
諾伊爾被部分媒體譽為當今及歷史上最好的守門員之一，且被視作為一位全面性及現代風格的守門員。[[Goal.com|Goal.com]]作家 Peter Staunton 認為諾伊爾是 "自[[列夫·耶辛|列夫·雅辛]]以來最好的守門員"。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ballon d'Or contender Neuer is the best goalkeeper since Yashin {{!}} Goal.com|url=https://www.goal.com/en/news/1717/editorial/2014/12/01/6671671/ballon-dor-contender-neuer-is-the-best-goalkeeper-since|accessdate=2020-10-07|work=www.goal.com|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922094158/https://www.goal.com/en/news/1717/editorial/2014/12/01/6671671/ballon-dor-contender-neuer-is-the-best-goalkeeper-since|dead-url=no}}</ref>

作為一位身材條件良好的球員，他被名宿及評論員認為他具有速度、體力、冷靜、專注力、心理素質及穩定表現的能力，可以處理球場上發生的所有情況。最為人所稱的是他出色的反應能力、擋球能力(無論是手或腿部)、靈活性、衝刺速度、腳法、攔截橫傳球及閱讀比賽的能力，並能在他的守備範圍內有效發揮。在場上必要時，他會充當清道夫的位置，利用速度來將球快速的清出，因此有著 "門衛(sweeper-keeper)" 的稱號。如此一來，可以使團隊的後防線向前推進，對守門員的定位有著革命性的影響。除此之外，在一對一及十二碼球的對抗當中也受名宿所稱讚。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Greatest of all time': Bayern ace hailed after Champions League masterclass|url=https://au.sports.yahoo.com/champions-league-final-manuel-neuer-best-goalkeeper-bayern-defeat-psg-220640582.html|accessdate=2020-10-07|work=au.sports.yahoo.com|language=en-AU|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010205332/https://au.sports.yahoo.com/champions-league-final-manuel-neuer-best-goalkeeper-bayern-defeat-psg-220640582.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Bayern Munich's Manuel Neuer: the goalkeeper-revolutionary who has changed the way we see football|url=https://www.bundesliga.com/en/bundesliga/news/manuel-neuer-bayern-munich-goalkeeper-revolutionary-changing-way-we-see-football-461172.jsp|accessdate=2020-10-07|work=bundesliga.com - the official Bundesliga website|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Is Bayern Munich's Manuel Neuer the best goalkeeper ever?|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11945/9846554/is-bayern-munichs-manuel-neuer-the-best-goalkeeper-ever|accessdate=2020-10-07|work=Sky Sports|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216031951/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11945/9846554/is-bayern-munichs-manuel-neuer-the-best-goalkeeper-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Benzema: "Neuer is the best goalkeeper in the world"|url=https://www.marca.com/en/2014/12/07/en/football/real_madrid/1417975914.html|accessdate=2020-10-07|date=2014-12-07|last=MARCA.com|work=MARCA|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404195836/https://www.marca.com/en/2014/12/07/en/football/real_madrid/1417975914.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Perfect player series: Building a flawless goalkeeper|url=https://www.thescore.com/chlg/news/1289056|accessdate=2020-10-07|last=Nesci|first=Gianluca|work=theScore.com}}</ref>

除了禁區內的表現，諾伊爾在手拋球及腳法上也有優異的發揮,能夠送出深遠的長傳來製造快速反擊的機會。他甚至認為憑著自己的腳法可已在德國的第三級聯賽中擔任中後衛的角色。在2015年時，義大利門將[[詹路易吉·布冯|布馮]]認為他是當時代最好的守門員之一。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=How a Manuel Neuer penalty could win the World Cup for Germany|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/13/manuel-neuer-goalkeeper-penalty-world-cup-germany|accessdate=2020-10-07|date=2014-07-13|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803205750/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/13/manuel-neuer-goalkeeper-penalty-world-cup-germany|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另一方面，一些德國媒體認為諾伊爾傾向在裁判做出判決之前就舉手警示裁判，創造出了Reklamierarm的單字來評論他。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Torwart-Reflex: Der ewige Reklamierarm von Manuel Neuer|url=https://www.welt.de/sport/fussball/bundesliga/fc-bayern-muenchen/article146217458/Der-ewige-Reklamierarm-von-Manuel-Neuer.html|newspaper=DIE WELT|date=2015-09-10|accessdate=2020-10-07|first=Lars|last=Wallrodt|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803191341/https://www.welt.de/sport/fussball/bundesliga/fc-bayern-muenchen/article146217458/Der-ewige-Reklamierarm-von-Manuel-Neuer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

